    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 5. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions are within the 15% acceptance threshold across all operating points. Package is submitted under the Minimal profile; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
